@section(Nitrogen Uptake)

Nitrogen Uptake model simulates how much nitrogen mass takes the plant from the soil. SAVANNA model  @cite(Coughenour1994) related to Nitrogen uptake is based on the Michaelis-Menten function of organic nitrogen concentration in the soil @cite(MichaelisMenten1913) . Nitrogen uptake can vary according to the availability in the soil and how it is distributed among the species.

